vars: {
  d2-config: {
    layout-engine: elk
    theme-id: 4
    pad: 40
  }
}

title: |'md
# Buffer Lifetime State Machine (io_uring)
**Critical Invariant:** A buffer in the `SUBMITTED` state is owned by the kernel. 
Userspace access during this window results in non-deterministic memory corruption.
'| {
  near: top-center
  style: {
    font-size: 24
    bold: true
    stroke-width: 0
    fill: transparent
  }
}

# ============================================
# STATE DEFINITIONS
# ============================================
# Bitmask Invariants: 
# [0] KERNEL_OWNED, [1] APP_OWNED, [2] DIRTY, [3] ERROR_BIT

states: {
  FREE: {
    label: "FREE\n─────────────\nREF_COUNT: 0\nBITMASK: 0000\n• Buffer in pool\n• RefCount == 0\n• Safe to Acquire\n• No Kernel Refs"
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#90EE90"
      stroke: "#228B22"
      stroke-width: 3
      border-radius: 15
    }
  }
  
  SUBMITTED: {
    label: "SUBMITTED\n─────────────\nREF_COUNT: 1 (K)\nBITMASK: 0001\n• SQE Linked\n• Kernel DMA Active\n• **LOCKED STATE**\n• No App Access"
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#FFD700"
      stroke: "#FF8C00"
      stroke-width: 5
      bold: true
      border-radius: 15
      shadow: true
    }
  }
  
  PROCESSING: {
    label: "PROCESSING\n─────────────\nREF_COUNT: 1 (U)\nBITMASK: 0010\n• CQE Reaped\n• App Owns Data\n• Read/Copy Safe\n• Pending Release"
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#87CEEB"
      stroke: "#4169E1"
      stroke-width: 3
      border-radius: 15
    }
  }
  
  ERROR: {
    label: "ERROR\n─────────────\nREF_COUNT: 1 (U)\nBITMASK: 1010\n• Operation Failed\n• CQE.res < 0\n• Needs Sanitization\n• Release Required"
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#FF6B6B"
      stroke: "#DC143C"
      stroke-width: 3
      border-radius: 15
    }
  }
}

# ============================================
# VALID TRANSITIONS (Numbered for TDD)
# ============================================

initial: {
  shape: circle
  label: "●"
  style.fill: "#228B22"
  style.stroke: "#228B22"
  style.font-color: white
  width: 30
  height: 30
}

initial -> states.FREE: "0. App Start" {
  style.stroke: "#228B22"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

states.FREE -> states.SUBMITTED: {
  label: "1. buffer_acquire()\n[io_uring_submit]"
  tooltip: "App provides buffer index to SQE and notifies kernel"
  style: {
    stroke: "#228B22"
    stroke-width: 3
  }
}

states.SUBMITTED -> states.PROCESSING: {
  label: "2. CQE Success\n[res >= 0]"
  tooltip: "Kernel writes completion data and releases DMA lock"
  style: {
    stroke: "#4169E1"
    stroke-width: 3
  }
}

states.SUBMITTED -> states.ERROR: {
  label: "2b. CQE Failure\n[res < 0]"
  style: {
    stroke: "#DC143C"
    stroke-width: 2
    stroke-dash: 3
  }
}

states.PROCESSING -> states.FREE: {
  label: "3. buffer_release()\n[Work Complete]"
  style: {
    stroke: "#228B22"
    stroke-width: 3
  }
}

states.ERROR -> states.FREE: {
  label: "3b. buffer_release()\n[Post-Cleanup]"
  style: {
    stroke: "#228B22"
    stroke-width: 2
  }
}

# ============================================
# ILLEGAL TRANSITIONS (Safety Boundary)
# ============================================

states.SUBMITTED -> states.FREE: {
  label: "❌ ILLEGAL: Early Free\nViolation: Use-After-Free"
  style: {
    stroke: "#DC143C"
    stroke-width: 4
    stroke-dash: 5
    animated: true
  }
}

states.PROCESSING -> states.SUBMITTED: {
  label: "❌ ILLEGAL: Double Submit\nViolation: Index Collision"
  style: {
    stroke: "#DC143C"
    stroke-width: 4
    stroke-dash: 5
    animated: true
  }
}

# ============================================
# DOCUMENTATION PANELS
# ============================================

bug_scenario: {
  label: |'md
## ⚠️ THE SILENT CORRUPTION BUG
**Timeline:**
1. **T0:** `IORING_OP_READ` submitted with `buf[X]`.
2. **T1:** App logic error calls `release(X)` while kernel is reading.
3. **T2:** Thread B acquires `buf[X]` and writes sensitive data.
4. **T3:** Kernel completes hardware DMA, overwriting Thread B's memory.

**Result:** Data corruption that never triggers a crash, only invalid state.
  '|
  shape: rectangle
  near: top-right
  style: {
    fill: "#FFF0F0"
    stroke: "#DC143C"
    stroke-width: 2
    border-radius: 8
  }
}

invariants: {
  label: |'md
## OPERATIONAL INVARIANTS
| Action | FREE | SUBMITTED | PROCESSING | ERROR |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---: |
| **Write** | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Read** | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Recycle**| ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |

*DMA ownership is atomic. Handover only occurs via CQE visibility.*
  '|
  shape: rectangle
  near: bottom-right
  style: {
    fill: "#F0F8FF"
    stroke: "#4169E1"
    stroke-width: 2
    border-radius: 8
  }
}